docs.title: Economy Update
docs.text: Hello all! Welcome to the economy update. This is a massive rework of the economy, with more updates following in the coming weeks.

docs.title: Rules Rework
docs.text: Discord rules and in-game rules have been reworked from scratch to better reflect the needs of our current community. Below you will find the new rules that all members are expected to follow at all times:
